-- Turkey’s Trabzonspor Says Hires Sol Bamba from Leicester City
-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 2012-06-18T08:40:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-18/turkey-s-trabzonspor-says-hires-sol-bamba-from-leicester-city.html
Trabzonspor, a Turkish first
division soccer club, said it hired defender Souleymane Bamba
from England’s  Leicester City .  Trabzonspor will pay 750,000 U.K. pounds ($1.2 million) to
Leicester for the contract, according to a statement from
Trabzonspor Sportif Yatirim & Futbol Isletmeciligi TAS, the
club’s listed unit.  Trabzonspor shares gained 3.7 percent to 11.35 liras at
11:05 a.m. in Istanbul, heading for the biggest increase since
June 1.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Benjamin Harvey in Istanbul at 
 bharvey11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
